name: Tic Tac Toe
tagline: This is a Tic Tac Toe game that I am using to explore JavaFX, Java, CSS, XML and FXML, and Neural Networks
body:
### Welcome to Tic Tac Toe.
This is a java program that allows the user to play against another user, the computer, or an ai (powered by a neural network!).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
